{
  "description": "A breathtaking view down a rocky streambed towards a towering granite peak shrouded in mist and clouds. The streambed is filled with various sized rocks and pebbles, with a shallow stream of water flowing between them. Dense evergreen trees line both sides of the streambed, creating a narrow, enclosed pathway. The peak in the distance appears massive and imposing, dominating the landscape. The sky is partially obscured by clouds, adding to the dramatic effect. The lighting is diffused, creating a soft, natural ambiance.",
